data.description:
Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom brick home with an office yours. 
As you enter, you're greeted by a thoughtfully designed floor plan that effortlessly connects the living spaces. The heart of the home is a cozy living room, featuring a brick fireplace that adds a touch of rustic charm. The highlight of this home is the dedicated office space, providing an ideal environment for remote work. Natural light floods the room, enhancing productivity and creating a welcoming atmosphere. 
NEW ROOF 2023. This home has storm shelter. 
Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort and style in Fayette living!
